id=ds_touch_keeper
name=Dual Screen Touch Keeper
version=v1.1.0
versionCode=2
author=KingAether
description=Stops the touchscreen on USB-C external displays from dying after a minute of inactivity. Targets the Retroid Dual Screen (RDS Touchscreen 222a:0001) by USB ID and disables its autosuspend, with a watchdog that re-applies on hotplug. Confirmed on AYN Odin 3.
